      <title>创纪录的债券销售热潮为高盛、花旗和摩根大通带来利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/record-bond-sale-spree-fuels-profits-for-goldman-citi-jpmorgan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着企业以创纪录的速度在美国出售债券，银行的盈利正在从承销费中获得提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/record-bond-sale-spree-fuels-profits-for-goldman-citi-jpmorgan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 18:19:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通在财报发布后开始销售大银行债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/jpmorgan-opens-spigot-big-bank-bond-sales-after-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司和富国银行Co.正在美国高等级债券市场发行132.5亿美元的新债，这是华尔街六大银行在发布第一季度业绩后可能进行的一系列债券发行中的第一笔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/jpmorgan-opens-spigot-big-bank-bond-sales-after-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:11:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>270% 涨势失败，特朗普媒体 53 亿美元抛售加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/trump-media-plunges-after-registering-shares-warrants-for-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)的社交媒体初创公司周一大跌，延续了两周的低迷状态，此前该公司迈出了允许前总统和其他内部人士利用其股份的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/trump-media-plunges-after-registering-shares-warrants-for-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 13:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着大型科技股抛售，标准普尔 500 指数跌破 5,100 点：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[零售销售火爆刺激人们押注美联储将不急于降息，债券收益率大幅上涨，科技股拖累股市。石油价格因地缘政治焦虑而大幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-in-wake-of-iran-attack-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 22:08:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
